Just figured I'd drop in and say hello to everyone since it's been like January since I've last posted on here. None of my close friends really post like they used to... LJ is played out.  It's still nice to jump on and see what everyones up to instead of taling to them (which would be hard living in West Virginia now).  I'll be back in O-Town around X-mas though... anyone know of any good shows for the holidays? 

Every morning I wake up there are cows across the road and deer running through the yard... I'm not used to this lol

Everyone keeps asking what the fuck I'M doing out in the middle of nowhere... One word :CHRIS

ta ta
~Ash

Shit has been going down... life sucks for me... I can't make decisions and I just don't know what to do... I've just been in hiding lately... People are turning their backs on me... Other people are popping back into my life and calling me and I don't know if thats good or bad. My car keeps falling apart... i get the belts fixed now its making another weird noise and not driving right... its idleing really low too... I'm not sure if I'm moving away anymore, I'm not sure about a lot of things.  All I know is that this month has been horrible and Ive gotten myself pulled into some bad things... drugs, too many drugs in the first 20 days of the year. Ive been keeping myself fucked up to make time go by faster.  I need help.  I think I need to go see someone. I can't stop crying...im so lost... someone help

Wow... what a night... Cliff is MAJORLY trashed and I had to drive him home... thats all I have to say on that subject.

I'm moving to West Virginia soon.  I'll miss everyone but I have something way to important up there.

I WISH I WAS UP NORTH RIGHT NOW =***(  *kitten whines*

well... night night

3 MONTHS since I've wrote on old LJ.  

Let me sum things up.  

WHATS NEW WITH ME:

*Charles and I got our own place a few months ago over on 436 by Sams club in Regency Oaks Apts...

*I've been working at Clipper Ship Pet Grooming since Sept 1st or so & I love it.  I was gonna quit for reasons I'd rather not say & my boss said she would give me a dollar raise so I took it.

*Halloween was major fun... can't give out details but lets just say i was fuuuucked the hell up & someone stole something off my porch... a little tin dog from the Briar Patch that I named Spork.  I was so pissed

*Got into a car wreck... had to buy a new radiator

*Got 2 cats from Pets Mart... Dookie & Pookie.  They are the coolest in the world

*Bo-gator (my savannah monitor) died like 2 weeks ago. I made Charles burry him with a pinky mouse. Im gonna get a skunk gecko soon.

*haven't done any photoshoots cuz Carahs been outta town... I miss the shoots and chillin with Carah =)

*This will be my first Thanksgiving alone... My mom will be on a cruise and the rest of my family is going to South Carolina.  I cant get off work.  So I don't know what I'm gonna do...

Okay... I don't know what else to say cept I got a new computer and I'm fixing to get the internet hooked up so I will be online everyday again pretty soon.... I MISS everybody...

---------------------------------------------------------------- Amby and I went to Daytona today... forgot it was Black College Reunion and got hit on by a bunch of thugs. haha but it was still fun cuz I got a nice tan n shit. I'm chillin with my mom right now... yes yes I miss her =) What's everyone doing tomorrow? I have no plans quite yet... no plans = beach again

Last night I finally watched The Ring... freaky shit... the freakier part was after we watched the video part in the movie and the phone rang... our phone rang and whoever called hung up. I cried last night... like forever. Charles just held onto me all night. I get little diabetic emotional breakdowns sometimes like "why me?", "what did I do". Yea, people see what I go through but they don't Feel it. I'm just sick of having to deal with shit but anyways.... I won't go into that. This whole waking up at 6:15 thing again sucks ass!!! School sux ass, but I gotta work my ass of this last semester so I can finally graduate and get tha fuck outa Criminal High. *falls asleep on the keyboard*

Charles n I are finally in our new home.  It's off 29th street in Sanford.  We live with his best friend Danny whom he works with.  It's cool cuz Charles gets to be around his god daughter all the time.  And Dannys mom lives here and she is the shit.  She makes us dinner every night & car rides with her are funny as fuck!  My puppy LOVES it here.  He has a huge yard to run in now & he's not left in a room by hisself 24/7 cuz he stays in our room.  Yesterday this dude came over and fed him a $20 nugget.  My dog was fuct the hell up.  He ate a bunch of beggin strips and 2 bowls of food and when this dude knocked his smirnoff over he licked it all up.  We cant be doing that all the time but it's funny every once in a while.  Hey, at least he slept on his Scooby pillow all throughout the night without waking us up for once.

I'm happier right now then I have ever been in my life.  Getting to cuddle up every single night with the person you wanna spend the rest of your life with is the best feeling in the world.  His touch is so comforting and all the little things he does for me.  I can't imagine my life without him ever. I've never been this much in love in my whole life. He IS the reason I wake up every morning knowing everythings gonna be ok.  I know you all are probablly thinking "oh, lets see how long this lasts", right?  Well, we will see... and I know you guys are gonna be amazed when 10, 20 years down the road the sparks between him and I havent changed one bit.  We are just perfect to a T like that.  O.K I'll stop with the mushy-ness.

---> Whitney!!! I'll call u in the morning tomorrow so we can chill, ok bebe?  & if anyone else wants to hang out anytime before sunday this week leave me a message on here and I'll call or get in touch somehow.  I <3 you all and hope you're spring break is rawkin it to the max.

xoxoxoxo

all the stuff at my house is pretty much packed up.  We are getting the apartment in like 2 weeks!!! YAY!

Yesterday was great! It was like a mini Spring Break reunion.  Marcus picked me up in the morning and we went out to eat chinese buffet then to SxB.  I got to see muh Josh-ness, Amanda-ness, & Melanie...  Me, Amanda & Marcus played Bomerman for a while.  Great shit! It was really nice to see them again.  I was gonna stay the night but I decided to get home to Charles... Him, Danny & Steph pulled up at like 10:30pm.  Jenn and I just got back from picking Chris up at Red Lobster & he was telling us that all the staff is fucking each other and it's full of drama.  He was saying how he is not gonna get in the drama but some shit appeared... kinda funny. lol.

I'm fixing to leave with Jenn to get breakfast and bring her fish back over by UCF.  If anyone needs to get ahold of me call 407-330-1238  <333333 yas!

Last night was total drama in my household.  My mom and I got into it and I feel really bad.  I love her so much but lately she doesn't understand me as well as she used to.  Charles was at work till midnight so I went to Jaymes & Shyannes new apartment and watched Jay & Silent Bob. BOOOOOOONG! Then I went home and Charles was home so we went to bed.  My dad came over this morning at like 8 and I got in the car.  He told me my mom called him this morning crying.  He brought me to school cuz mom aparently wasnt going to.  I love him to.  I feel closer to him lately for once in years.  It's his birthday and it kinda made me feel bad cuz his eyes were tearing up.  We all feel like the family is falling apart.  Today when I get home I'm gonna start packing some boxes up to move.  Charles and I are getting a 1 bedroom apartment in like 2 weeks.  Calie and Chris are getting a 2 bedroom apartment in the same place too.  so me, Charles, Chris, Cali, Scott, Jaymes, Shyanne & Kalaya will all be in the same apartment complex.  It will rock cuz we can all hang out and stay awake till 4 am every morning! Tonight I'm going out to dinner with the familt for my dads b-day then I'm going back to Calis.  I don't even wanna step foot in my house right now. Jenn Rivera is picking me up from school and we are bringing our pit bull pups to the dog park together.  Bogator misses his brother. 

Anyways... off to 3rd period... Spring Break Thursday after school!!!
HAPPY BIRFDAY @ MUH DADDYNESS (46) & TO CHARLES (24)!!! woop woop!

went to school this morning and got into my first period computer class... I just started thinking and started crying.  I had my dad check me out.  I'm at home now, horrible stomach cramps, a trembling heart.... and I can't stop crying.  I havent left Sanford i like 3 months it seems.  I went downtown with Jenn Friday.  Her and I are drifting away it seems.  My best friend Anjy moved away to Cocoa over a year ago and she hasnt got in touch with me. I'm a mess.

I'm torn... I don't know what to do think or say anymore.  I feel like a horrible person.  For the first time in my life... I feel bad for myself....

<CENTER>
"Do you care if i don't know what to say
will you sleep tonight or will you think of me
will I shake this off pretend its all okay
that there someone out there who feels just like me
there is  </CENTER>

I'm moving out in like 2-4 weeks.  I'll still be living in sanford.  Me, chris & Charles are gonna get an apartment and bring my puppy.  They have breed restrictions (no pit bulls),,, but mine is pit/rot so he's not a pit he's a MUTT!!! ohhhh yea, I'm so happy.  The place has 2 bathrooms too so we all dont have to argue.  I get along with Chris and Charles so well.  We never argue... it's all fun.  The 3 of us watched Alladin at like midnight wednesday...fun times.

So yeah... i'm really happy cuz I got a new puppy Tuesday.  He's a 6 week old brindle pit bull.  My friend Jenn Rivera got his brother (the runt) and we are gonna have thme play togeher a lot, take them to the dog park n all. He is soooo adorable.  I originally named him Chaos but inside jokes led to his name being Bo-gator *re-shnitzled, you're gonna be my dietary supplement, 2 llamas climbing up a mountain".  Oh, ignore that. So yea... We took them to Petsmart Wednesday and I let him pick out his own toy... It's this rope thing and I got him a  collar that I know he'll just grow out of in a month or so. His paws are huge cuz he has 25 % rot in him.  He's gonna be around for a long time and I NEED to raise him correctly so he wont bite people.  Most pits are either very sweet or very aggressive.  Mine shows a lil of both so far.  He's already chewing on metal! He is pretty much potty trained already.  He goes to the door when he wants out.  I have him ont h ebest puppy food possible (Pro Plan) and hes a pig. He loves Kalaya (my freinds 4 month old baby). Hes kinda protective over her already. The 2 cats don't really like him. He's so cute when he sleeps next to you.  Last night he was laying exactly like charles.  right leg on the side of the sofa, left leg straight n all.  I'm taking him to get all his shots in the next week which Charles is paying for. I'll get pics of him on here as soon as I get the time. Oh, and I'm moving in 3 weeks.  I need a car, a job, and well... a life, but at least I got my dog, right???
